{"1":[[1138,1317,"What a shocker!"],[1317,1359,"The bears"],[1359,1463,"shut down Casper Atkinson"],[1463,1559,"and the Ice Wolves,"],[1559,1764,"breaking their five-game streak."],[1764,1881,"The lce Wolves couldn't get anything"],[1881,1960,"past the defense,"],[1960,2031,"it's like the Bears"],[2031,2227,"were reading their minds!"],[3053,3207,"You sold our plays to the Bears,"],[3207,3274,"didn't you?"],[3332,3574,"No, I... I didn't."],[3574,3657,"Never see you at"],[3657,3924,"any of the late night practices, Jenna."],[3966,4074,"I would never, I..."],[4220,4404,"Chad says that he saw you"],[4404,4554,"on the Bears side of town last night."],[4617,4746,"So if you weren't in bed with them,"],[4746,4921,"then what the hell else were you doing?"],[4975,5105,"Maybe you should ask Chad."],[5105,5230,"Oh, good one, yeah."],[5342,5555,"We're fucking gods at this school."],[5555,5651,"What do you think everyone's gonna do"],[5651,5843,"when they find out that you sold us out?"],[5872,5985,"They're all gonna hate you."],[6051,6177,"Just like Casper."],[6197,6331,"He'll never be MVP."],[6352,6531,"He'll never make it to the NHL."],[6531,6735,"It'll be all your fault!"],[6827,6969,"I would never hurt Casper."],[7027,7115,"Yeah, right."],[7157,7290,"You ghosted him last year."],[7290,7465,"You made him a laughing stock."],[7499,7682,"But now, he's the king of the school"],[7682,7928,"and you're a sad little janitor."],[7953,8224,"I bet that this is your petty revenge."],[8224,8270,"And we know"],[8270,8383,"that you're hiding something."],[8491,8571,"Search her bag."],[8958,9071,"No one can know"],[9071,9217,"that I'm secretly a stripper."],[9267,9359,"That I dance to pay"],[9359,9551,"for my little sister's medical bills."],[9876,10068,"Woah!"]],"2":[[0,108,"That’s ugly as fuck."],[108,212,"Oh, you wear this, Jenna?"],[212,262,"What are you,"],[262,367,"a stripper or something?"],[925,1071,"I always knew you were nothing"],[1071,1230,"but a little fucking whore."],[2456,2