 with me?"],[4149,4275,"I couldn't tell him the truth then,"],[4275,4371,"and I can't now."],[4416,4508,"Because my secret"],[4508,4675,"would destroy everything."],[5359,5501,"Ladies and gentlemen,"],[5501,5580,"this is the moment"],[5580,5764,"you've all been waiting for."],[5797,6139,"Please give it up for Angel!"],[6168,6322,"Yeah girl, get it!"],[6348,6527,"By day, I'm Jenna."],[6552,6673,"A broke college student"],[6673,6781,"trying to get by."],[6844,7048,"All alone except for my sister, Wendy."],[7073,7307,"But at night, I become Angel."],[7353,7465,"I put on this mask"],[7465,7574,"and dance for my money,"],[7574,7799,"all so I can keep my little sister alive."],[7853,8053,"Casper hates me for what I did to him,"],[8053,8258,"but he's a senator's son."],[8258,8383,"A hockey star."],[8383,8475,"He could never be"],[8475,8608,"with a stripper like me."],[8608,8883,"And he can never know my secret."],[8996,9159,"Woo! Yeah!"],[9159,9313,"Look at that."],[9388,9651,"She seems... familiar."],[10089,10247,"Casper?"]],"6":[[633,717,"Daddy's home."],[1372,1476,"What the hell"],[1476,1714,"is Casper Atkinson doing here?"],[1714,1826,"Whatever happens,"],[1826,1997,"he can't see me up close."],[2081,2239,"Your phone has been going off all night."],[2515,2644,"Ruby, I need more shifts."],[2656,2848,"They found a donor match for my sister,"],[2848,3011,"but I need to come up with $10,000"],[3011,3111,"to pay for the down payment"],[3111,3199,"on the surgery."],[3228,3378,"Then you’re going to have to"],[3378,3611,"reel in some nice big fish tonight."],[3687,3749,"Come on."],[3845,4012,"Gentlemen!"],[4012,4162,"As you all know,"],[4162,4412,"Angel doesn't do private dances."],[4471,4746,"But tonight, for one night only,"],[4746,4992,"we're going to auction off one hour"],[4992,5167,"with our star performer"],[5167,5321,"in the VIP room."],[5321,5438,"Yeah!"],[5438,5538,"Woo!"],[5659,5734,"Ruby, you know that I don’t"],[5734,5822,"do private dances"],[5822,5914,"not after