r?"],[4679,4879,"I'm a dancer, not an escort."],[4967,5063,"I'm not for sale."],[5113,5292,"He's still the same arrogant prick"],[5292,5459,"I broke up with a year ago."],[5526,5597,"Fair enough."],[5718,5843,"What about the identity, then?"],[6135,6239,"How much for the mask to come off?"],[6327,6506,"He can't find out who I really am."]],"9":[[429,517,"No touching."],[583,654,"Naughty boy."],[1334,1451,"Do I need to be punished?"],[1572,1668,"Oh, yeah..."],[1743,1801,"You do."],[2936,3144,"You may have won the auction."],[3219,3382,"But you're mine tonight."],[3570,3628,"Yes."],[3753,3853,"Yes, what?"],[3899,3978,"Yes, Angel."],[4475,4533,"So..."],[4662,4821,"Why did you pay for me anyway?"],[4963,5067,"Trying to get your mind"],[5067,5188,"off someone else?"],[5301,5459,"Something like that..."],[5513,5634,"You know I'd believe you"],[5634,5747,"if you told me the truth."],[6118,6352,"There's this... girl."],[6439,6598,"She's... stubborn."],[6677,6748,"Doesn't listen."],[6906,7157,"Knows exactly how to piss me off."],[7157,7378,"Is he talking about me?"],[7624,7699,"Wrong answer."],[7841,8003,"What you're supposed to say..."],[8087,8216,"is no, Angel..."],[8283,8470,"You're the only one I want."],[8612,8675,"Say it."],[8729,8933,"Say, I want you, Angel."],[8933,9075,"I want you, Angel."],[9396,9647,"She smells just... like Jenna."]],"10":[[137,387,"She smells just... like Jenna."],[483,575,"There's no way someone"],[575,713,"so self-righteous and uptight"],[713,863,"would work at a place like this."],[925,1121,"I need to get Jenna out of my head."],[1142,1242,"I'm ready, Angel."],[1292,1405,"I want what I paid for."],[1459,1522,"Oh yeah?"],[1822,1943,"How bad do you want it?"],[2027,2210,"Are you willing to beg for it?"],[2252,2339,"I'll do anything."],[2410,2469,"Please, Angel,"],[2469,2531,"dance for me."],[2802,2919,"Well, that's too bad, isn't it?"],[3036,3098,"The hell?"],[3228,3324,"I paid for you."],[3415,3440,"What?"],[3440,3503,"You want more money?"],[3