t the fuck is wrong with you?"],[2419,2565,"You beat the shit out of me last night"],[2565,2677,"over a damn stripper."],[2677,2786,"Because you fucking deserve it."],[2786,2948,"Only a coward like you hits women."],[3148,3294,"Knock it off, guys."],[3294,3353,"Come on."],[3453,3549,"We have a game tomorrow."],[3624,3716,"Not worth getting benched over."],[3716,3762,"Go."],[3920,4054,"Dude, chill the fuck out."],[4054,4120,"Leon!"],[4183,4379,"Mess with captain one more time"],[4404,4512,"and we'll kick you off the team."],[4658,4767,"I'm not scared of him."],[4846,5005,"If it weren't for his senator daddy,"],[5005,5088,"he'd be a nobody."],[8216,8279,"Careful there."]],"38":[[642,792,"He probably sprained his shoulder"],[792,913,"last night fighting Leon."],[955,1042,"And he doesn't even know"],[1042,1172,"it was me he saved."],[1330,1476,"Is your shoulder bothering you?"],[1655,1851,"I, I know, some"],[1851,2085,"physical therapy if it would help."],[2398,2444,"Yeah."],[3449,3557,"Are you just using this"],[3557,3703,"as an excuse to check me out?"],[3858,3949,"Get over yourself."],[3999,4074,"I'm done."],[4074,4175,"You can put your clothes on."],[4704,4984,"It actually feels a lot better."],[5217,5321,"Where'd you learn how to do that?"],[5543,5684,"My sister is bed ridden"],[5684,5918,"so I learned a few skills"],[5918,6093,"to keep her muscles from weakening."],[6302,6468,"I didn't know, I’m-"],[6468,6544,"That's fine."],[6727,6840,"I should get back to work."],[6990,7236,"I actually wanted to ask you something."],[7799,7903,"What happened here?"]],"39":[[667,746,"I bumped it."],[829,975,"It's none of your business."],[975,1234,"Why are you always so prickly with me?"],[1493,1589,"Are you hiding something?"],[1985,2210,"You know if you say you hate me"],[2210,2423,"I might just never speak to you again."],[2711,2827,"So you don't hate me?"],[2969,3094,"That doesn't mean I like you."],[3303,3415,"Then I'll make you like me."],[4254,4333,"Oh, you see the new"],[4333,4412,"assistant doctor?"],[4441,4512,"Yeah, to think there’s"],[4512,4612,"a dude up in- - Watch where"],[4612,4688,"you’re going."],[5192,5305,"Hey you know who she kind of"],[5305,5380,"reminds me of?"],[5409,5568,"Whatever you're about to say"],[5609,5689,"I don't wanna hear it."],[5772,5964,"That stripper, Angel."],[6031,6114,"You know Angel?"],[6126,6256,"Nah, her ass is definitely"],[6256,6356,"not tight enough for that."],[6477,6669,"Can you guys shut the fuck up please?"],[6819,6886,"Jesus."],[6886,7002,"Assholes, both of you."],[7903,7970,"Jenna?"],[8116,8179,"Oh my God."],[8179,8237,"Aaron?"],[8345,8425,"Hi!"],[8717,8825,"It's been what - Wow!"],[8825,8950,"like 12 years?"]],"40":[[66,162,"It's been what, - Oh my..."],[162,367,"like, like 12 years"],[367,425,"since you got"],[425,487,"adopted? - Yeah."],[575,629,"Wow."],[654,834,"It's so good to see you."],[917,1013,"What are you doing here?"],[1121,1338,"My adoptive dad's a doctor."],[1418,1493,"So here I am"],[1493,1655,"interning with a hockey team."],[1847,1951,"Who the hell is that?"],[2331,2456,"Do you want something?"],[2515,2606,"I need to talk to you."],[2606,2686,"It's important."],[2777,2894,"Hey, hey, hey, hey!"],[2894,3011,"Dude, you're hurting her."],[3028,3115,"Who the hell are you?"],[3115,3278,"Mind your own business, pal."],[3482,3578,"I'm her friend."],[3578,3636,"Really?"],[3687,3782,"That's funny because"],[3782,3916,"she's never mentioned you"],[3916,4033,"and I'm the most important person-"],[4033,4158,"Casper, that's enough!"],[4337,4416,"What do you need?"],[4558,4625,"I got the dean"],[4625,4750,"to give you another scholarship."],[5013,5113,"Are you serious?"],[5113,5171,"Thank you."],[5284,5338,"Um..."],[5451,5593,"Let's catch up later, Aaron."],[5593,5797,"Just call me if you need anything."]],"41":[[654,779,"I thought we were going to"],[779,955,"sign scholarship papers."],[1021,1167,"I lied about the papers."],[1167,1251,"I signed them already."],[1251,1443,"You'll get the money"],[1443,1534,"deposited every month."],[1534,1693,"Then why did you drag me in here?"],[1814,1947,"You seemed awfully happy"],[1947,2085,"with that guy over there."],[2122,2273,"How come you never smile at me like that?"],[2273,2431,"Because Aaron is my old friend"],[2431,2585,"and you're just a pain in my ass."],[2619,2927,"Oh, so me getting Serena off your back"],[2927,3078,"and stopping you from getting expelled"],[3078,3282,"doesn't, doesn’t even deserve"],[3282,3386,"a little smirk?"],[3695,3862,"Look, he may make you smile,"],[3862,4133,"but do you give him massages"],[4133,4391,"and kiss him in bathrooms?"],[5000,5059,"What do you mean?"],[5142,5230,"You're mine."],[5301,5347,"And I don't want"],[5347,5497,"to share you with anyone."],[5551,5663,"Including him."]],"42":[[141,200,"You're just used to"],[200,283,"getting what you want."],[354,504,"You don't actually mean that."],[546,629,"You just want to win."],[763,930,"Look me in the eye and say that again."],[1030,1163,"We would never work, Casper."],[1163,1230,"I'm not interested"],[1230,1330,"in being some Cinderella"],[1330,1438,"and I don't want to play"],[1438,1539,"whatever game this is."],[1539,1718,"This isn't a game, Jenna."],[1860,1989,"I should have hated you for the way"],[1989,2277,"you treated me a year ago, but..."],[2277,2356,"I can't."],[2498,2690,"I really am in love with you, Jenna."],[2731,2773,"And I'm not going to"],[2773,2898,"let some stupid doctor"],[2898,2982,"get in the way of that."],[3161,3207,"I don't know"],[3207,3349,"what you want me to say, Casper."],[3349,3457,"Say you want me too."],[3490,3574,"Say that you-"],[3987,4225,"Jenna, your sister needs surgery now."]],"43":[[1197,1372,"The surgery went perfectly."],[1564,1676,"Thank you, Dr. Brown."],[1726,1918,"I'm sure Wendy will be thrilled to see you"],[1943,2052,"and your handsome boyfriend."],[2052,2106,"Oh, he's not-"],[2106,2181,"Thanks, Doc."],[2786,2836,"Jenna?"],[2886,3053,"I missed you so much."],[3161,3319,"Your surgery was a success."],[3361,3432,"Hi, Wendy."],[3536,3620,"I'm Casper."],[3732,3841,"I know you."],[3949,4070,"You're that hockey player."],[4070,4204,"Jenna used to watch your games"],[4204,4287,"all the time."],[4287,4354,"Wendy, don't."],[4354,4554,"She was obsessed with you last year."],[4554,4733,"Always talking about your muscles"],[4733,4950,"and your hair, and your eyes."],[5176,5230,"And..."],[5317,5426,"maybe I'm confusing you"],[5426,5513,"with someone else."],[5555,5618,"I doubt it."],[6844,6994,"Now that Wendy's awake, you can go."],[7111,7207,"I'm sure you're busy."],[7298,7374,"Not at all."],[7411,7515,"Wendy's great company."],[7640,7795,"Is it okay if I stay, or..."],[7807,7991,"I love hockey."],[7991,8116,"It's my favorite sport."],[8187,8350,"If you make it to the NHL,"],[8350,8487,"can I get free tickets?"],[8525,8600,"Whatever you want."],[8650,8779,"As long as you bring your sister, though."],[9009,9154,"Wendy, you know that it's too risky"],[9154,9242,"with your health."],[9547,9726,"Well, lucky for you,"],[9726,9855,"I know of a rink we can rent out."],[9905,9976,"What if we..."],[10068,10164,"brought the game to you?"]],"44":[[1476,1555,"Hey."],[1597,1805,"Thank you so much, Casper."],[1805,1976,"This is the best day of my life."],[2006,2093,"No problem."],[2110,2189,"Maybe when you're better,"],[2189,2273,"I'll teach you how to play."],[2377,2444,"No way,"],[2444,2544,"that would be amazing."],[3015,3203,"Thank you, Casper."],[3203,3278,"I mean it."],[3499,3557,"Look..."],[3591,3674,"I'm sorry for being a jerk"],[3674,3787,"with the whole Aaron thing earlier,"],[3787,3878,"I'm just..."],[3995,4112,"I’m glad I could make it up to you."],[4546,4646,"Does that smile mean"],[4646,4754,"you don't hate me anymore?"],[4954,5080,"Not today, at least."]],"45":[[588,692,"Did you want something?"],[821,900,"Look, I'm grateful"],[900,1038,"that you brought Wendy to the rink,"],[1038,1130,"but that doesn't mean that I'm-"],[1130,1201,"But you're..."],[1234,1297,"What?"],[1305,1543,"I didn't quite catch that, you're..."],[1543,1589,"What?"],[1780,2014,"I said, I'm grateful."],[2014,2185,"You know, every time you smile like that,"],[2277,2385,"I want to do this."],[3428,3499,"If you want to walk away,"],[3499,3599,"now's your chance."],[3670,3724,"But I'm not going to"],[3724,3853,"let you push me away again."],[4825,5034,"You taste exactly how I remember..."],[5109,5184,"Sweet."],[5242,5330,"Casper!"],[5422,5547,"We need to talk!"]],"46":[[859,1234,"So you skip a charity fundraiser,"],[1309,1418,"so you could hang out"],[1418,1584,"with some poor scholarship student?"],[1584,1726,"Dad, the amount of money she has"],[1726,1872,"doesn't define her worth."],[1872,1964,"Really?"],[2014,2252,"I lost out on raising thousands,"],[2289,2489,"thousands of dollars"],[2489,2748,"because of her distracting you."],[2769,2831,"I'm sorry,"],[2831,2969,"but it's not her fault, Dad."],[2969,3107,"Do you really care about her?"],[3211,3511,"Because if you do, I'm cutting you off."],[3603,3853,"I will not have some gold digger"],[3853,4175,"steal our family money or ruin my..."],[4254,4562,"I mean, our reputation"],[4562,4733,"right before my re-election."],[4821,4921,"If I don't shut him up now,"],[4921,5080,"he'll never stop going after Jenna."],[5125,5192,"Dad, what..."],[5313,5405,"what I have with Jenna,"],[5405,5526,"it's, it's nothing."],[5526,5793,"I would never stoop for someone so"],[5868,5980,"low class."],[6106,6164,"Good."],[6456,6606,"Because you deserve better."]],"47":[[1121,1184,"Jenna."],[1255,1401,"I just forgot my gloves."],[1401,1493,"What did, what did you hear?"],[1493,1593,"Everything."],[1710,1860,"Forget what I said earlier."],[1914,2068,"You really are a jerk, Casper."],[2068,2152,"I only said all that"],[2152,2289,"to get my dad off your back."],[2289,2398,"I was just, I-"],[2398,2481,"Or, what, what?"],[2481,2565,"He wouldn't let you"],[2565,2727,"use his black card anymore?"],[2727,2882,"Jenna,