nna."],[1910,2010,"I'm gonna prove it to you."],[2239,2298,"Sure."],[2406,2594,"Aaron, I would love to be your date."],[2736,2877,"Hopefully none of those hockey jerks"],[2877,2957,"ruin our day."],[3703,3862,"Anything else, Mr. Atkinson?"]],"50":[[1092,1242,"What is up, Cappy?"],[1301,1376,"Dude, you're acting like"],[1376,1551,"a moody little bitch."],[1551,1697,"Watch your fucking mouth, dude."],[1801,1889,"Exhibit A."],[2018,2068,"Dude."],[2068,2285,"Is this about that poor janitor girl?"],[2623,2681,"Trust me, bro."],[2681,2752,"She is not worth"],[2752,2861,"blowing the team up over."],[2969,3061,"Say one more word"],[3061,3178,"and you're off the team, asshole."],[3269,3357,"Whoa, whoa."],[3357,3424,"Damn, bro."],[3424,3541,"You gotta lighten up."],[3595,3687,"And I think I know"],[3687,3849,"just what you need, buddy."],[3903,4066,"Alright, alright, alright."],[4099,4158,"Ferda."],[4212,4275,"Ladies and gentlemen,"],[4275,4366,"gather around."],[4366,4604,"I have a special little game to play."],[4667,4821,"It's called beer strip pong."],[4821,4900,"Uh-huh."],[4913,4996,"Alright, the rules of the game"],[4996,5088,"are pretty simple."],[5088,5401,"My boy Casper over here versus..."],[5463,5530,"Aaron?"],[5555,5605,"Aaron."],[5605,5651,"Something like that."],[5651,5809,"Yeah, Aaron."],[5943,6056,"Rules are pretty easy."],[6072,6172,"Throw the ball in the cup."],[6172,6277,"Once when you make it in,"],[6277,6368,"your opponent has to"],[6368,6514,"lose a layer of clothing."],[6569,6660,"Wish me luck?"],[6660,6744,"You're gonna need it."],[7307,7436,"How about you take your shirt off?"],[7457,7582,"Or are you too"],[7582,7682,"scared to measure up?"],[7820,7887,"Nah."],[7937,8078,"Nothing to be afraid of."]],"51":[[2118,2277,"Not so impressive now, are you, Doc?"],[2402,2469,"I don't know."],[2535,2681,"Jenna seemed pretty impressed."],[2694,2748,"Really?"],[2798,2857,"Cause it looks like"],[2857,2940,"she's been staring at me"],[2940,3028,"this entire time."],[3082,3199,"Casper, come on."],[3244,3415,"So that is one point each,"],[3415,3516,"which means..."],[3666,3858,"next one wins it."],[4667,4729,"Guess you're my"],[4729,4833,"good luck charm, huh?"],[5209,5263,"Watch where you're"],[5263,5351,"putting your hands, buddy."],[5351,5447,"Man, let her go."],[5447,5613,"She told me she doesn't want you."],[5663,5722,"Really?"],[5722,5943,"You think she wants you, Dr. Know-It-All?"],[5943,6143,"She friendzoned you years ago, bro."]],"52":[[25,175,"Yeah, I think she would."],[175,304,"She told me everything about you"],[304,417,"and how she can't stand you"],[417,604,"because you're a meat-headed jock"],[604,763,"who can't even satisfy her."],[763,838,"Aaron!"],[1376,1459,"Stop it!"],[1651,1710,"What the hell"],[1710,1826,"is wrong with both of you?"],[1889,1968,"I'm done with this."],[1968,2060,"Jenna, wait."],[2127,2293,"You embarrassed me in front of everyone."],[2293,2402,"They're all gonna be talking about this"],[2402,2448,"at school tomorrow."],[2448,2531,"Let them talk."],[2673,2765,"You're the only person"],[2765,2890,"I care about, Jenna."],[2927,3057,"I know you care about me, too."],[3069,3215,"I do care, but I shouldn't."],[3228,3340,"He's a senator's son"],[3340,3516,"and I'm a secret stripper."],[3516,3649,"We can't be together."],[3649,3807,"It's better if we hate each other."],[3807,3995,"I want you, Jenna."],[4099,4229,"And I'm not afraid to prove that"],[4229,4341,"in front of everyone else here."],[5034,5134,"Are you crazy?"],[5134,5280,"You're the one driving me crazy."],[5280,5372,"Casper, why can't you just"],[5372,5463,"leave me alone?"],[5505,5551,"Fine."],[5693,5797,"If that's really what you want,"],[5864,5993,"we'll never talk again."],[6673,6848,"I told you that in confidence, Aaron."],[6848,6973,"How could you use that to turn-"],[6973,7057,"Don't tell me you actually"],[7057,7173,"do care about him."],[7173,7374,"I was just telling the truth."],[7374,7511,"He's not good enough for you."],[7511,7678,"You don't get to decide that for me."],[7803,7932,"You are just as bad as him."],[8324,8437,"I thought you were my friend,"],[8437,8521,"but I guess not."],[9655,9730,"Where's Angel?"],[9784,9868,"I need to see her."]],"53":[[100,175,"Where's Angel?"],[225,296,"I need to see her."],[325,496,"Oh, I'm sorry, sir."],[496,633,"Angel is not performing tonight."],[859,1105,"Actually, she just quit."],[1167,1272,"She was saving money"],[1272,1393,"for her sister's surgery"],[1393,1547,"and it was a success."],[1689,1839,"But she will be performing"],[1839,1972,"one more night on Saturday"],[1972,2072,"if you want to catch her."],[2072,2239,"Wait, her sister is sick?"],[2239,2293,"Yeah."],[2323,2452,"That's why she started stripping."],[3028,3103,"Could it be?"],[3157,3324,"Is Jenna... Angel?"],[4091,4312,"That's my MVP right there."],[4325,4529,"What a fucking win, dude."],[4650,4725,"I swear."],[4783,4867,"This is what happens"],[4867,4988,"when you stop letting punk bunnies"],[4988,5063,"distract you."],[5100,5263,"I want her to tell me the truth."],[5305,5451,"I want to know if she's Angel,"],[5451,5689,"but I told her I'd leave her alone."],[6865,7098,"You've been quite the busy girl,"],[7098,7223,"haven't you, Jenna?"],[7294,7415,"Everyone is talking about"],[7415,7536,"those two guys"],[7536,7674,"who were fighting over you"],[7674,7786,"at the pool party."],[7786,7962,"Quite the it girl"],[7962,8087,"these days, huh?"],[8220,8500,"Yeah, more like gold-digging tramp."],[8787,9092,"You're stuck here serving people"],[9092,9317,"in your ugly little outfit"],[9380,9547,"while Casper ignores you."],[9597,9818,"I guess your 15 minutes of fame"],[9818,9889,"are over."],[9914,10130,"Serena, if you want Casper so bad,"],[10168,10256,"you can have him."],[10297,10414,"If he's ignoring you too,"],[10414,10548,"well then that seems like"],[10548,10681,"a personal problem."],[10769,10977,"Oh, and my uniform might be ugly,"],[10977,11182,"but at least my personality isn't