's a reason that"],[6986,7136,"it didn't work out the first time."],[7232,7369,"Is that really how you feel, Angel?"],[7711,7811,"Or should I say Jenna?"]],"65":[[663,779,"How did you find out?"],[925,996,"The tattoo."],[1192,1330,"I had a feeling when I saw it."],[1409,1526,"And then my dad"],[1526,1618,"showed me the photo."],[1747,1897,"But I didn't know for sure until now."],[1897,2064,"So you came here to humiliate me?"],[2093,2298,"I came for an explanation, Jenna."],[2560,2669,"Why didn't you tell me?"],[2761,2806,"What?"],[2865,2948,"That I'm a stripper?"],[3040,3157,"So that you could look at me"],[3157,3236,"in disgust?"],[3307,3465,"So that you could embarrass me"],[3465,3595,"in front of the whole student body"],[3595,3728,"and have the dean expel me?"],[3728,3878,"I had no other choice!"],[4116,4333,"I did it for money for Wendy's surgery."],[4333,4471,"Her life depended on it."],[4471,4650,"I would have done anything to save her."],[4721,4850,"That's the reason you stood me up"],[4850,4946,"that night at the dance?"],[5075,5201,"I thought you hated me."],[5201,5301,"No..."],[5301,5509,"oh God, I could never hate you."],[5676,5805,"You were my dream, you..."],[5876,5993,"you made my heart race."],[5993,6160,"You gave me butterflies."],[6272,6385,"But we would never work."],[6564,6744,"You're the senator's son, and I'm..."],[7023,7273,"If you knew what happened that night,"],[7273,7353,"you would understand."],[7353,7440,"I do know."],[7469,7624,"I know exactly what happened that night."]],"66":[[233,392,"I know exactly what happened that night."],[467,525,"So..."],[625,721,"That night..."],[759,900,"Angel wanted to leave early"],[900,1017,"to go for a date."],[1051,1176,"But this one customer"],[1176,1272,"wouldn't let her go."],[1338,1434,"He even hit her."],[1555,1705,"I was so scared for her."],[1743,1885,"She’s like a daughter to me."],[2047,2239,"But then her sister's condition,"],[2239,2364,"got worse and then,"],[2364,2523,"she needed cash first.